---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Abonnements - Admin KoproGo">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Gestion des Abonnements</h1>

      <div class="bg-yellow-50 border-l-4 border-yellow-400 p-4 mb-6">
        <div class="flex">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-yellow-400" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M8.257 3.099c.765-1.36 2.722-1.36 3.486 0l5.58 9.92c.75 1.334-.213 2.98-1.742 2.98H4.42c-1.53 0-2.493-1.646-1.743-2.98l5.58-9.92zM11 13a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zm-1-8a1 1 0 00-1 1v3a1 1 0 002 0V6a1 1 0 00-1-1z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="ml-3">
            <p class="text-sm text-yellow-700">
              Cette page est en cours de développement. La gestion des abonnements sera bientôt disponible.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-6 mb-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Plans d'abonnement prévus</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          <div class="border-2 border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">🌱 Starter</h3>
            <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary-600 mb-4">49€<span class="text-sm text-gray-500">/mois</span></p>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
              <li>✓ Jusqu'à 3 immeubles</li>
              <li>✓ 50 lots maximum</li>
              <li>✓ Support email</li>
              <li>✓ Gestion de base</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="border-2 border-primary-500 rounded-lg p-6 bg-primary-50">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-2">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">🚀 Pro</h3>
              <span class="bg-primary-600 text-white text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded">Populaire</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary-600 mb-4">149€<span class="text-sm text-gray-500">/mois</span></p>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
              <li>✓ Jusqu'à 15 immeubles</li>
              <li>✓ 300 lots maximum</li>
              <li>✓ Support prioritaire</li>
              <li>✓ Fonctionnalités avancées</li>
              <li>✓ Rapports personnalisés</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="border-2 border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">💼 Enterprise</h3>
            <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary-600 mb-4">Sur devis</p>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
              <li>✓ Immeubles illimités</li>
              <li>✓ Lots illimités</li>
              <li>✓ Support dédié 24/7</li>
              <li>✓ API personnalisée</li>
              <li>✓ Formation incluse</li>
              <li>✓ SLA garanti</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Fonctionnalités à venir</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
          <li class="flex items-center">
            <span class="mr-2">💳</span>
            <span>Vue d'ensemble des abonnements actifs</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center">
            <span class="mr-2">📊</span>
            <span>Statistiques MRR et churn rate</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center">
            <span class="mr-2">🔄</span>
            <span>Gestion des renouvellements</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center">
            <span class="mr-2">⚠️</span>
            <span>Alertes pour les paiements échoués</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center">
            <span class="mr-2">📈</span>
            <span>Upgrade/downgrade de plans</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-6">
        <a href="/admin" class="inline-flex items-center text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-700">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 19l-7-7m0 0l7-7m-7 7h18"/>
          </svg>
          Retour au dashboard
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
